# ── Secrets — never commit these ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Google OAuth client secret JSON (downloaded from Google Cloud Console).
# The secret itself lives only as a Supabase Edge Function secret — this
# downloaded JSON file is the source you copied it from, and must never
# land in this repo, public or private.
client_secret_*.json
*.client_secret.json
google-credentials.json
google-oauth-secret.json

# Any local environment / secrets files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.pem
*.key
secrets.json

# Supabase service_role key if ever exported to a file (anon key is the
# only key that belongs in the client-side app — service_role must never
# appear in this repo under any filename)
service_role*.json
supabase-service-key*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
*.swp

# Local backups you don't want tracked
*.backup.html
*.bak
